text: Mespelbrunn is a community in the Aschaffenburg district in the Regierungsbezirk of Lower Franconia (Unterfranken) in Bavaria, Germany and a member of the Verwaltungsgemeinschaft (municipal association) of Mespelbrunn, whose seat is in Heimbuchenthal. ==References== ==Other websites== * Mespelbrunn Castle Category:Aschaffenburg (district)
title: Mespelbrunn
